				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Technically, it is <em>possible</em> to create pages named with SCP numbers higher than 1999, but there'd be no place to put them on the Series 2 mainlist.</p> <p>Hence &quot;Remember to fill out 1000-1999 before going higher!&quot;</p> <p>Edit: What Dmatix said. Basically, the note is a reminder to not go over 1999, since we haven't reached the 2000s block yet.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
